<hw>manicotti</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Tubular large noodles that are
usually stuffed with mild cheese and baked in tomato sauce; -- a type of
Italian <isa>pasta</isa>; also a dish of such noodles thus
prepared.</def>⟦br⟧
